race.description: Sky Racing (N/P) Tg 5+W Series 3 F Pr2 Division1
race.comment: JUST ZORRO (7) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at this track but was a Other winner two back at Gawler. Will find this more suitable and can atone. KING CORDITE (2) jumped from this box last time and also the same course and distance when a one length second (20.22) in a Other. Key chance on best form. ANTECEDENT (5) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (20.14) at this track in a Other over 342m. Must be included in calculations. BINGO QUEEN (4) has won at this course and distance so worth including. Something for the Multiples: HUXI BEAR (9)
